info.name: Youtube - Blue and flat all over
info.description: A darkblue theme for Youtube with a hint of green. If you are looking for a theme that goes together better with the new Youtube layout as of 2014, try out Youtube - Onewox Redesign. Screenshots: What to Watch Channel Video Footer I recommend downloading the "Walkway Semibold" font for the logo, for the best experience
info.additionalInfo:
Helpful replies is appreciated
